pageProduct.name: Vita Bubs Kids Brain Health Goat Milk + DHA Omega 3 60 Chewable Tablets
pageProduct.description:

General Information

Vita Bubs Goat Milk + DHA Omega-3 is a premium formulation to support brain health, cognitive function, learning and information processing in the early school years, eye health and nervous system health. Contains Easy to Digest Australian Goat Milk. With natural berry flavour for a great tasting children's formulation!

Vita Bubs is brought to you by Bubs, trusted by Australian families and dedicated to children's nutrition. The Vita Bubs range is based on scientific evidence and is proudly Australian Owned and Made.

Suitable For: 2 - 12 years

Size: 60 chewables

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each chewable tablet contains:
Concentrated Fish Omega-3 Triglycerides 189.5mg
Docosahexaenoic Acid (DHA) 100mg
Eicosapentaenoic Acid (EPA) 6.6mg
Goat Milk 200mg

Contains: Contains Lactose, Gluten, Sucralose, Sulphite, Soya beans and Phenylalanine.

Allergen Contains: Gluten| Lactose| Phenylalanine| Soybean| Sulphites

Directions

Children 2 - 6 years: Chew one tablet daily, during or immediately after a meal under adult supervision, or as directed by a healthcare professional.
Children 7 - 12 years: Chew two tablets daily, during or immediately after a meal under adult supervision, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25C. Do not sure if seal under lid is broken or missing.
